{"tid":1242233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"903狂叫人登記做選民同投票","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:36:40.000Z","uid":8439,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e9ef6af97224a759d0ee353a225fe2f5e9b0632","tid":1242233,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"森美之前又係係早霸王叫人記得投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15267eb33151c97fd2746508dbe74298ce00a043","tid":1242233,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:38:12.000Z","msg":"今次903真係幫到盡"},{"pid":"c69994a75262401a28f3a90c65ef7e8da9506eb7","tid":1242233,"uid":221265,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"咁係真<br />\n好多人以為自己登記咗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有一大班換咗新身份證嘅俾人取消咗選民資格<br />\n<br />\n真係要佢哋check自己嘅選民身份仲存唔存在"},{"pid":"a32a86cbdda48868bb9a0a2cd38e6aa20f95ff57","tid":1242233,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9054863fa10593ca9c1f7119edba30121a0ad72a","tid":1242233,"uid":3255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:44:54.000Z","msg":"有冇人有時間搵搵上屆區議會啲<br />\n爭幾十票險勝嘅資料<br />\n<br />\n可以做啲文宣... <br />\n等啲人知道.. <br />\n其實爭佢一票真係可以爭好遠<br />\n快啲2/7前登記同一定要投票"},{"pid":"65f656d3bf686b37f704afd8b5c0ded5d31c5467","tid":1242233,"uid":244412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"keep 住 宣傳未做選民架巴打 一定要做選民"},{"pid":"0e8b1635d1afb77ca7048f44b7df2a7324c72f19","tid":1242233,"uid":203794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"903算係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講得咁出 13/6嗰日啲節目調動先西利 唔怕廣告商唔落廣告 但係反觀港台 班廢中廢老仲喺度乜事都冇咁 繼續開心玩開心笑"},{"pid":"e08a6fea495510e20bd2392f68741063086ac212","tid":1242233,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"905486